race.comment: AMRON TOMMY (1) was a last start winner this course and distance taking a Grade 5 in 26.09 in the best time on the card and clocking a personal best as well. In form and looks the one to beat again. MIA NEO (5) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner three back (26.18) at this track over 460m. Expected to do much better this time. NEED YOU NOW (7) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 460m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Winning chance. SUPERFLY GIRL (2) can run a bold race on best form.
